data.description: Move-in ready in the desirable lake community of Water's Edge. Welcome, to a well-designed split planned home with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. This beautiful property is smartly spaced w/ a flex area (currently being used as a baby room) and formal dining room. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, granite countertops and an eat-in breakfast room. The family room is open to the dining area and kitchen creating easy access and space for entertaining. Located in the rear of the home, the comfortable primary bedroom has a walk-in closet as well as an additional storage closet. The primary bathroom has double sinks, a soaking tub and separate shower. Step unto the covered patio where the backyard is fully fenced and large enough to create your outdoor fun. The home has updated flooring and light fixtures. Water's Edge is home to 2 parks, clubhouse, fitness center, pool, walking trails and lake.
